allorsUnifiedGood.name: AIR MARREL LAM3500
allorsUnifiedGood.description:
The LAM 35000 is a 35 tons capacity self-propelled heavy duty main deck loader offering the most advanced features required by the end users, including clear deck for handling oversized loads.

The LAM 35000 complies with international safety regulations. It is able to operate under severe weather conditions.

Its drive system has been designed to allow the loader excellent inching characteristics, easing aircraft approach

Although designed as a heavy duty main deck loader the LAM 35000 is also suitable for use of lower deck to handle pallets.
